{"tid":408481,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"召集拍開片嘅你","createTime":"2017-09-21T08:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T13:52:38.000Z","uid":62225,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64dad8507769cb2153805dc271a32f98c2e25148","tid":408481,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:53:53.000Z","msg":"[戴頭盔mode] 今次係真宣傳！<br />\n<br />\n搞緊個短片創作比賽，希望用短片形式收集青少年嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前其實開左一堆post知道好多巴絲對拍片剪片有興趣，所以都係到借個位宣傳下。推介呢個比賽俾有心嘅巴絲參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單，2-6 mins 既片，類型不限。想透過大家鍾意短片呢個興趣去帶起呢一個主題比唔同既人去睇！<br />\n真心勿小，有好東西同大家介紹下only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面有活動詳情: <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/OeZUfbGsnmQ0xsMu2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FOeZUfbGsnmQ0xsMu2&d=MhMkvgyz0adl4zSqwv%2B4df1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=600bb472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/OeZUfbGsnmQ0xsMu2</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw，大家有咩ideas或者困難都可以係呢個post集思廣益一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180ce3940c31e970fb06fc83b6fa2260cf91885f","tid":408481,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"估唔到隻痴膠港獨獸屌打手真係有用"},{"pid":"a7f1634b54eb1fe650059b7870865aa1db7bf6d2","tid":408481,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae908b9fad901c97612216a8e4490e6cb536a0e8","tid":408481,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep